{"product_id":"magrada-peach-plump-lip-balm-10ml","title":"Magrada Peach Plump Lip Balm 10ml","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"entry-content\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eIndulge your lips with this luscious lip balm, enriched with botanical oils for that perfect shine. If you crave maximum hydration and irresistibly soft, plump lips, this balm is just for you! Immerse yourself in the delightful notes of fresh peach, perfectly blended with nourishing candelilla wax, olive oil, castor oil, and vitamin E. Unique formula not only restores your lips’ natural softness but also locks in moisture for a fuller, more vibrant look. Plus, you can feel good about your choice—our fully recyclable packaging keeps your beauty routine eco-friendly.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003eApply to clean lips as desired. Perfect for use as a nourishing lip balm before applying lipstick or as a glossy finish over lip balm or lip liner.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients: \u003c\/strong\u003eHydroxystearic\/Linolenic\/OleicPolyglycerides, Olea Europaea (Olive) Fruit Oil, Ricinus Communis (Castor) Seed Oil, Glycerin, Candelilla Cera, Polyglyceryl-3 Diisostearate, Hydrogenated Castor Oil, Dipalmitoyl Hydroxyproline, Tocopherol (Vitamin E), Linalool, Limonene\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eIngredients of natural origin: 100%\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe list of ingredients may be changed. Please see the packaging for the updated and most accurate list of ingredients.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eparaben-free \u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e sulphate-free \u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e silicone-free \u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e alcohol-free \u003cspan\u003e| \u003c\/span\u003evegan \u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e cruelty-free \u003cspan\u003e| \u003c\/span\u003ewith a minimal list of ingredients\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"Magrada Organic Cosmetics","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50848815579463,"sku":null,"price":10.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/magrada-peach-plump-lip-balm-10ml-427278.png?v=1739897251","url":"https:\/\/bioskina.com\/products\/magrada-peach-plump-lip-balm-10ml","provider":"bioskina","version":"1.0","type":"link"}